1684033614.query:
WITH bpoly AS (
    SELECT
        ST_Setsrid (ST_GeomFromGeoJSON ('{"type": "MultiPolygon", "coordinates": [[[[7.818124, 13.859122], [7.835312, 13.859122], [7.835312, 13.872538], [7.818124, 13.872538], [7.818124, 13.859122]]]]}'), 4326) AS geom
)
SELECT
    Date_trunc('month', valid_from) AS month,
    Count(*)
FROM
    contributions c,
    bpoly b
WHERE
    ST_Intersects (c.geom, b.geom)
    AND (status_geom_type).status = 'latest'  -- excludes deleted
    AND (tags @> '{"station": "subway"}')
GROUP BY
    month
ORDER BY
    month;

WITH bpoly AS (
    SELECT
        ST_Setsrid (ST_GeomFromGeoJSON ('{"type": "MultiPolygon", "coordinates": [[[[7.818124, 13.859122], [7.835312, 13.859122], [7.835312, 13.872538], [7.818124, 13.872538], [7.818124, 13.859122]]]]}'), 4326) AS geom
)
SELECT
    Date_trunc('month', valid_from) AS month,
    Count(*)
FROM
    germany_15 c,
    bpoly b
WHERE
    ST_Intersects (c.geom, b.geom)
    AND (status_geom_type).status = 'latest'  -- excludes deleted
    AND (tags @> '{"station": "subway"}')
GROUP BY
    month
ORDER BY
    month;
